title: GS Blockchain
author: GS Blockchain
content: The US represenptatives of Genesis have met the investment manager from BlueRun Ventures and conducted an in-depth discussion on the development prospects of the decentralized commerce.  Founded in Silicon Valley in 1998, BlueRun Ventures is an early stage venture capital firm, focuses on seed and series A investments in key markets with a specialized focus on mobile, fintech and real time data systems. Its overall management scale currently exceeds1 billion dollars, and the successful investments include: PayPal, Waze, Topsy, Chomp, Slide etc.
